Nykøbing Falster.title: Nykøbing Falster
Nykøbing Falster.byline: Nykøbing Falster is a city on the island of Falster in the south eastern part of Denmark with just short of 20,000 citizens.

Nykarleby.title: Nykarleby
Nykarleby.byline: Nykarleby (Finnish: Uusikaarlepyy) is a town and municipality in Ostrobothnia.
